{"tid":2509160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"商品背景　巴士車身大賣廣告，來自中國の偽日本品牌","createTime":"2021-04-29T08:51:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T09:45:38.000Z","uid":261647,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9040bd805420f6cf28b0d6218543eff51e16efff","tid":2509160,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:51:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fcwithyou/posts/271965101258690\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffcwithyou%2Fposts%2F271965101258690&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwWAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=e0c65a8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fcwithyou/posts/271965101258690</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVsKnKHaLY1QYT6dfZxjZtGM9Vs4YgPmxE2wFpnLeSgwb?filename=MWhEUZU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMWhEUZU.jpg&h=fbc2d646&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作者：和你 FC<br />\n<br />\n▸商品背景◂ 巴士車身大賣廣告，來自中國の偽日本品牌<br />\n<br />\n最近呢三個日用品廣告大量出現喺巴士車身，分別係「ar F&Uuml;M 紡優美」、「NA Shampoo 奈十八本」及「Ka ポッド &bull; 王子菁華」，牌子名同廣告內容都大量使用日文字，而其中「ar F&Uuml;M」仲有個㗎妹聲優做代言。驟眼睇，絕對會覺得係日本貨<br />\n<br />\n但事實係呢三個牌子都係 2000 年成立於廣州，假扮來自德國嘅中國品牌「威露士」旗下，呢三個牌子嘅產品，全線喺日本根本就冇得賣<br />\n<br />\n呢三個牌子過半產品都係中國或泰國生產※，但部分產品標榜日本製，又係乜回事？<br />\n<br />\n其實威露士的確喺日本開咗間分公司，可以睇番日本政府旗下「日本貿易振興機構」2017 年嘅報道◎，威露士開呢間分公司，係為咗可以得到「日本製」嘅無形價值。一開始係會由其他廠代工，預計五年後會有自己工廠。<br />\n<br />\n五年都就快過去，依家仲係大部分產品唔係日本製，加上個重點都係：日本根本冇得賣！<br />\n<br />\n※ 根據 HKTV Mall 產地標示<br />\n<br />\n◎ 「日本貿易振興機構」2017 年報道<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jetro.go.jp/en/invest/newsroom/2017/dfb977f7e2f7e371.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jetro.go.jp%2Fen%2Finvest%2Fnewsroom%2F2017%2Fdfb977f7e2f7e371.html&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwWAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=43a56229\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.jetro.go.jp/en/invest/newsroom/2017/dfb977f7e2f7e371.html</a><br />\n<br />\n#和你FC #商品背景 #威露士 #Walch #Centralin #中國公司 #中國品牌 #中資 #威萊 #Whealthfields #王子石鹸 #Ouji #PRINCE #arF&Uuml;M #紡優美 #Na #NAShampoo #奈十八本 #Ka #Kaポッド #王子菁華"},{"pid":"67396b58329c4b1e7d64b6632575942d1a479c73","tid":2509160,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:53:39.000Z","msg":"屌你而家啲支那牌子成日扮日本野 點分"},{"pid":"ddb7f77859f87856489642175f748a8e40ca7e53","tid":2509160,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T08:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edf26808c6f66e29096d3bc391f137cf0a3d62f6","tid":2509160,"uid":133806,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:00:31.000Z","msg":"見佢搵花澤支菜就知啲支那仔始終搣唔甩浸味啦<br />\n<br />\n講真日本大牌子搵代言，起碼都新垣結衣綾瀬遥石原里美呢啲，要後生少少都搵廣瀬姊妹橋本環奈，甚至乃木坂嗰類先啦<br />\n<br />\n幾可會搵個聲優呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要係支那仔最鍾意捧嗰個花澤支菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd26cacc195c5e87da72e998ecd4a5009ca8326","tid":2509160,"uid":393276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:03:36.000Z","msg":"早兩日仲買咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d61019a79e3147ccf08738c2ca3f2229cac242","tid":2509160,"uid":224323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa7e44abe5ff194b79d7020e465e177334e0a1b","tid":2509160,"uid":62247,"like":0,"